N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4053.1 - Daily report of racing results

State Regulations

The judge or judges shall, at the close of each day's
racing, sign and send a report of the result of each race to the office of the

National Steeplechase and Hunt Association and the
commission. Notes
